data.description: This is your chance to rent a charming mid-century bungalow in the heart of Seminole Heights. This home has it all: curb appeal in the front, space and privacy in the back! It sits on a large 7,750sq/ft corner lot with ample parking on the side. You'll fall in love with the front porch with the swing before even walking in. Upon entering you're greeted with lots of natural light coming in from the skylights in the tall vaulted ceiling above. The home features an open floor-plan from the front foyer to the kitchen all the way in the back. Inside the kitchen you'll find stainless steel appliances and granite counters. Off of the kitchen is a large utility room with an included washer/dryer as well as plenty of pantry space. There is a full bathroom en-suite to the master bedroom as well as a half-bathroom off of the common space. Both bathrooms are recently renovated and brand new. Let your four-legged friends stretch their legs in the huge manicured back-yard with a covered rear porch and wooden shed. Call today to schedule an appointment!
